{"tid":2370802,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Timable 定 Playwhat?","createTime":"2021-01-18T09:42:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T11:19:06.000Z","uid":390161,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5a03096639ebdbd7ad12837b0e60a7318cfe10e2","tid":2370802,"uid":390161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:42:26.000Z","msg":"大家有無聽過Timable 同Playwhat?<br />\n<br />\n最近發現兩個好似嘅網站，都係俾人搵吓放假有咩玩，有咩打卡位，有咩Workshop 可以報名之類。<br />\n<br />\n我求其cap咗幾張圖，想吸引大家入去兩個網站到摸索吓，睇吓大家覺得邊個好用啲？<br />\n<br />\n搜尋篇<br />\n<br />\n1.\tTimable (<a href=\"http://timable.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftimable.com%2F&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS%2F3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=fb527886\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://timable.com/</a>) <br />\n<br />\n有4個items俾你揀，包括活動日期，咩類型，咩地點，係俾情侶定獨L去嘅都有得揀。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gkfpdS0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgkfpdS0.jpg&h=7ac7e513&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8qMf40U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8qMf40U.jpg&h=ee11be0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dvnu9sD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDvnu9sD.jpg&h=a9b3b439&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xrim0zn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXrim0zn.jpg&h=7de05ce0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9EHZNer.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9EHZNer.jpg&h=24100c2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n用後感：<br />\nTimable 有好多個活動分類俾你揀，如果你有啲好Specific嘅活動想搵嘅，可以試吓Timable。<br />\n<br />\n補充：不過Timable就相對有好多廣告，隔幾個活動就見到一個廣告。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.\tPlaywhat (<a href=\"http://playwhat.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fplaywhat.hk%2F&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS%2F3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=693f37ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://playwhat.hk/</a>)<br />\n<br />\n呢個就相對簡單，得活動日期、類型、價錢俾你揀。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hZxbDmf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhZxbDmf.jpg&h=dfe8c476&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n用後感：Playwhat相對無咁多活動嘅分類，得6大類，包括工作坊、義工、藝術、線上活動等。<br />\n<br />\n我發現工作坊、義工呢兩類係有碌極都碌唔曬咁多嘅選擇。所以，如果你想搵多啲工作坊、義工之類嘅活動，可以試吓Playwhat。<br />\n<br />\n補充：Playwhat無廣告。<br />\n<br />\n大家鍾意Timable 俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，鍾意Playwhat 俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"6dd6c189f6a89f1b0a7841da4033f396ddd36be6","tid":2370802,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:43:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"488b37e3ac589a1c89b43ee01d952116559eedd5","tid":2370802,"uid":390161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6dd6c189f6a89f1b0a7841da4033f396ddd36be6","tid":2370802,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:43:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:45:45.000Z","msg":"Matt 哥留言好surprise <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f019b91a8311f98f2a5f66c753b0ac568c8be4b","tid":2370802,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"488b37e3ac589a1c89b43ee01d952116559eedd5","tid":2370802,"uid":390161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6dd6c189f6a89f1b0a7841da4033f396ddd36be6","tid":2370802,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:43:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:45:45.000Z","msg":"Matt 哥留言好surprise <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:46:04.000Z","msg":"點解<img src=\"/